              <p class="text-purple-600 font-black">8.2/10 ¬∑ $23-65/mo ¬∑ The Design Consistency Champion</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-black text-green-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Strengths</p>
              <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-600">‚úì</span><span>Gorgeous typography: best in class</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-600">‚úì</span><span>Beautiful gallery templates: photographers love it</span></li>
